.TH BUDDYDRIVE-GUI 1 "April 2025" "BuddyDrive"
.SH NAME
buddydrive-gui \- GTK4 desktop application for BuddyDrive
.SH DESCRIPTION
BuddyDrive GUI is a GTK4 desktop application for monitoring and configuring BuddyDrive, a peer-to-peer encrypted folder synchronization tool.
.PP
The GUI provides:
.IP \(bu 2
Real-time sync status monitoring
.IP \(bu 2
Folder management (add/remove folders)
.IP \(bu 2
Buddy management (pair with friends)
.IP \(bu 2
Configuration settings
.IP \(bu 2
Log viewer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B buddydrive-gui
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.buddydrive/config.toml
Configuration file (shared with buddydrive CLI)
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR buddydrive(1)
.SH AUTHOR
Goran Krampe <goran.krampe@gmail.com>
